u.s. credit for ecuador switch to veg oil the commod credit corpor ( ccc ) switch five mln dlr in credit guarante to ecuador to provid for more sale of u.s. veget oil , the u.s. agricultur depart said . the credit guarante were previous earmark for sale of u.s. cotton , feedgrain and wheat . the action reduc the guarante line previous author for sale of cotton from 1.5 mln dlr to 500,000 dlr , for feedgrain from four mln to two mln and for wheat from 45 mln dlr to 43 mln dlr and increas coverag for veget oil sale from two mln to seven mln dlr , the depart said .